text: Gunnar Wingqvist (7 May 1885 - 30 December 1918) was a Swedish diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre platform event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1885 births Category:1918 deaths Category:Swedish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Sweden Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Norrköping
